            "Mandatory": false,
            "DefaultValue": "",
            "Description": "ID of your Google Cloud project for Google Cloud API usage and billing. If no value is provided, the project ID defined in your Google Cloud service account is used. For this parameter to work, make sure to grant the \"Service Usage Consumer\" IAM role to your Google Cloud service account.",
